tldr: The agent successfully implemented several new features and addressed
  missing functionalities in the sleep questionnaire application. This included
  adding a tiredness severity scale, detecting COMISA and Insufficient Sleep
  Syndrome, integrating outbound resource links, implementing weighted EDS
  scoring, expanding CSV export, and incorporating pain and chronic fatigue
